snippet.title: Angelina Jolie Warned Johnny Depp About Dating Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Angelina Jolie Warned Johnny Depp About Amber Heard And How Dating Her Was A Bad Idea!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

For the past several years, Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard have been in an endless legal battle. Amber was and has been falsely accusing Johnny of physical and psychological abuse. Jonny has presented a lot of evidence, in this case, to pry his innocence and unmask all the lies that Amber has told that have caused him so much personal and professional harm. One of those pieces of evidence was audio where Amber and Johnny are heard arguing, and she mentions that she does not punch him, but only slaps him in the face. Johnny lost credibility and important roles in Hollywood due to Amber's accusations, and even some celebrities left his side, but there are some others who have not stopped supporting him, as well as his ex-partners, his family, and it can even be said that the famous actress Angelina Jolie.
